===Etymology===
Late Latin '[[crypticus]]', from {{Gr.}} '[[kruptikos]]', from '[[kruptos]]' (''hidden''), from '[[kruptein]]' (''to hide'').

===Adjective===
#Having hidden meaning.
#Mystifying or of an obscure nature.
#Involving use of code or cipher.

